[us_EN]
Final Strike to change the conditions of use 
(please do not patch at the same time with other keys modified)	

To use Final Strike, subject to the following conditions:
1, The magician holding a Staff of Wizardry.
2, The magician's xp is more than 300,000.
3, The magicianas has a Spellbook LV.9.

Meet the above requirements, switch to the  LV.9 Magic,
Hold down the start button and use LV.9 magic, there will be a Final Strike


After using, Staff of Wizardry will disappear, all player's hp variable 1, 

[zh_CN]
改变Final Strike条件

(最好不要与其他按键补丁混用）

修改者：e107

要使用Final Strike，需满足以下条件：
1、魔法师手持Staff of Wizardry
2、魔法师本人xp在300000以上
3、有LV.9魔法书

满足以上条件后，切换至LV.9魔法处
按住start键施放LV.9魔法 即为Final Strike

使用后，Staff of Wizardry消失，所有游戏者的hp变1的副作用仍然保留。

